# API integration

- Follow `docs/07_API_CONTRACT.md`.
- Use `VITE_API_BASE_URL`; never hardcode localhost or production URLs.
- All network calls go through the shared Axios client.
- Preserve FastAPI `detail` error support.
- Do not expose, return, log or persist post passwords.
- Do not silently rename response fields.
- If backend and specification differ, report the mismatch before adding compatibility code.
- Components must support loading, empty and error states.
